properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Okaloosa-Walton County Line to Pensacola FL out 20 NM; Coastal waters from Pensacola FL to Pascagoula MS out 20 NM
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 2 at 8:09PM CST until January 3 at 10:00AM CST by NWS Mobile AL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to one mile or less.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Pensacola FL to Pascagoula MS out
20 NM and Coastal waters from Okaloosa Walton County Line FL
to Pensacola FL out 20 NM.

* WHEN...Until 10 AM CST Friday.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 AM CST FRIDAY... ...SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IS CANCELLED
